<p>Christa is a  beautiful and sensitive young woman.  Initially very shy, she becomes outgoing and very sociable when  comfortable with a situation.She loves  to read funny books, watch television and go to the mall with friends.She loves Alabama football. She enjoys going to church and sings in the  choir.She would love to be able to take  dance lessons.Christa does average work  in school but she would benefit from adoptive parents who would actively  encourage and support her studies.Christa is very anxious to be adopted but she will likely be cautious as  she learns to trust her new family. She says she wants a &quot;'nice family&quot;  who &quot;don't yell&quot; and who will understand and accept her  unconditionally.Christa was born in  March , 1998. </p>
